  <entry>
    <title>无线传感网项目</title>
    <link href="/2025/02/16/%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BC%A0%E6%84%9F%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/"/>
    <url>/2025/02/16/%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E4%BC%A0%E6%84%9F%E7%BD%91%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-感知层设计"><a href="#1-感知层设计" class="headerlink" title="1 感知层设计"></a>1 感知层设计</h1><h3 id="1-1-CC2530简介"><a href="#1-1-CC2530简介" class="headerlink" title="1.1 CC2530简介"></a>1.1 CC2530简介</h3><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4cea0d0e0a243d4009b51.png" alt="11" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d1b8d0e0a243d4009b69.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d225d0e0a243d4009b6d.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d2bed0e0a243d4009b71.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><p>在这里我们看一下SFR关键字的作用:<br>sfr全称为：special function register（翻译为：特殊功能寄存器）</p><p>sfr P1 &#x3D; 0x90，就是把单片机的地址0x90改名字为P1，方便我们使用</p><p>一个弄明白后，剩下的一堆，你就懂了</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">sfr P1 = <span class="hljs-number">0x90</span>;<br>sfr P2 = <span class="hljs-number">0xA0</span>;<br>sfr P3 = <span class="hljs-number">0xB0</span>;<br>sfr PSW = <span class="hljs-number">0xD0</span>;<br>sfr ACC = <span class="hljs-number">0xE0</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2-LED亮灭"><a href="#1-2-LED亮灭" class="headerlink" title="1.2 LED亮灭"></a>1.2 LED亮灭</h3><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d5a2d0e0a243d4009b7a.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d6dfd0e0a243d4009b7c.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;"><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b4d773d0e0a243d4009ba8.png" alt="image.png" width=600  style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;">]]></content>
    
    
