  <entry>
    <title>stm32基础例程</title>
    <link href="/2025/02/15/2-%20stm32%E4%BE%8B%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <url>/2025/02/15/2-%20stm32%E4%BE%8B%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-LED驱动"><a href="#1-LED驱动" class="headerlink" title="1.LED驱动"></a>1.LED驱动</h1><p><strong>1.1 驱动形式</strong><br>在LED两端加载电压，使得LED有电流经过，驱动LED发光。因此只需要在LED两端形成电压差即可</p><p><strong>1.2 原理图</strong><br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b08c14d0e0a243d4ffa8b3.png" width=500></p><p><strong>1.3 功能</strong><br>IO口有8种模式：<br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b08f5ed0e0a243d4ffa956.png" width=300><br>其中GPIO用到的有5种。模拟输入是AD转换使用。推挽复用和开漏复用模式用于GPIO外的其他外设功能，比如SPI。</p><p><strong>1.4 推挽和开漏输出的区别</strong><br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b09007d0e0a243d4ffa987.png" width=500></p><ul><li><p>开漏模式，IO口内部没有上拉电阻，没有接MOS管，所以开漏电路不能输出高电平；要输出高电平，需要外部接上拉电阻，如果外部上拉电阻接的电压不是芯片IO电压，就相当于实现了IO口电平转换功能。</p></li><li><p>比如，推挽模式下，IO口输出高电平就是3.3V，用开漏模式，外部接电阻上拉到5V，那么输出高电平就是5V。</p></li><li><p>电平转换速度指芯片0&#x2F;1翻转的速度。</p></li><li><p>线与，两根IO直接连接在一起，电平按照与逻辑。通常用在一些可挂载多设备的总线上，比如I2C。</p></li><li><p>第二，SMT32的IO有速度需要配置</p></li></ul><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b0905fd0e0a243d4ffa9ad.png" width=500><p>如果不知道如何选，全部用50M，功能肯定正常。但是可能会增加耗电。<br>Tips</p><ul><li>普通功能的IO，通常2M就可以了。</li><li>如果一个IO用作I2C通信，速度通常就10K到400K，选10M就好了。</li><li>如果是用作SPI功能，可能会到20M速度，那就要选50M了。</li></ul><p><strong>1.5 例程源码</strong></p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">// 文件名: Led.c | 作者: 学不会傅里叶 | 日期: 2025-02-15 | </span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;stm32f10x.h&quot;</span>                  <span class="hljs-comment">// Device header</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdbool.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;led.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LED_PIN  GPIO_Pin_13</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LED_PORT GPIOC</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  最小系统板板载LED初始化</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Led_Init</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>  GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;<br>  RCC_APB2PeriphClockCmd(RCC_APB2Periph_GPIOC, ENABLE);<br>  <br>  GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_Out_PP;<br>  GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = LED_PIN;<br>  GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;<br>  GPIO_Init(LED_PORT, &amp;GPIO_InitStructure);<br><br>&#125;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  设置端口高低电平</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Led_Set</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">bool</span> state)</span>&#123;<br>GPIO_WriteBit(LED_PORT,LED_PIN,state?Bit_RESET:Bit_SET);<br>&#125;<br><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  LED灯亮</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Led_On</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>Led_Set(<span class="hljs-literal">true</span>);<br>&#125;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  LED灯灭</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Led_Off</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;<br>Led_Set(<span class="hljs-literal">false</span>);<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>1.6 注意点</strong><br>代码中使用三目运算符进行端口输出定义，同时引入的bool变量需要引入头文件&lt;stdbool.h&gt;</p><h1 id="2-按键"><a href="#2-按键" class="headerlink" title="2.按键"></a>2.按键</h1><p><strong>2.1 原理图</strong></p><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b096f6d0e0a243d4ffaaa0.png" width=300><p><strong>2.2 驱动原理</strong></p><ul><li>按键按下可能会持续100ms，那这个while循环可能执行了几十万次，那LED也循环了几十万次的亮灭状态，在按键释放的那一刻，此时LED的亮灭状态，是不可控的，因此需要增加按键释放等待</li><li>按键按下会有硬件抖动，硬件抖动的示意图如下（参考来源自baike.baidu.com），前沿抖动是按键按下的时候，按键弹片和接触点的抖动，释放则是同理，这是物理的限制，很难通过按键的艺优化去解决，对于按键抖动的问题，以上代码没有有效处理</li></ul><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b09637d0e0a243d4ffaa8e.png" width=300><p><strong>2.3 例程源码</strong></p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-comment">// 文件名: Led.c | 作者: 学不会傅里叶 | 日期: 2025-02-15 | </span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;stdbool.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;stm32f10x.h&quot;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;key.h&quot;</span></span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> KEY_PORT    GPIOB</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> KEY_PIN     GPIO_Pin_10</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  按键初始化</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">key_init</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span><br>&#123;<br>    GPIO_InitTypeDef GPIO_InitStructure;<br>    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Mode = GPIO_Mode_IPU;<br>    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Pin = KEY_PIN;<br>    GPIO_InitStructure.GPIO_Speed = GPIO_Speed_50MHz;<br>    GPIO_Init(KEY_PORT, &amp;GPIO_InitStructure);<br>&#125;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  判断按键是否按下，按下接地，不按下上拉</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 按下的时候返回true，不按下的时候返回false</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">key_pressed</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> GPIO_ReadInputDataBit(KEY_PORT, KEY_PIN) == Bit_SET;<br>&#125;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">/**</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @brief  等待按键按下结束</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @param  无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  * @retval 无</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">  */</span><br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">key_wait_release</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">void</span>)</span><br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (key_pressed());<br>&#125;<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>main.c中对按键输入的处理</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (key_pressed())<br>    &#123;<br>        delay(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (key_pressed())<br>        &#123;<br>            led_toggle();<br>            key_wait_release();<br>            delay(<span class="hljs-number">10</span>);<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="3-中断"><a href="#3-中断" class="headerlink" title="3.中断"></a>3.中断</h1><p><strong>3.1 如何理解中断(重点是理解保存CPU现场和恢复CPU现场)</strong><br>例子1：快递员送快递<br>场景设定<br>想象一下，你是一个在家学习的人，你坐在桌前专心写论文。然而，你也在等待一个重要的快递。现在，我们将把这个场景和中断机制做一个类比。<br>主程序<br>你写论文的过程可以看作是你的主程序。这是你在正常情况下一直在做的事情。<br>中断<br>快递员的到来就是一个中断事件。当快递员按门铃时，你必须暂停手头的工作（写论文），去开门签收快递。这一过程就是一个中断处理过程。<br>中断控制器<br>你的大脑就是中断控制器。它决定了你何时暂停写论文去处理快递员的到来。<br>中断详细过程</p><ol><li>主程序运行：你坐在电脑前写论文（主程序正在运行）。</li><li>中断事件发生：快递员按门铃（外部中断事件发生）。</li><li>保存现场：你记下当前代码写到哪一步了（保存CPU现场），以便回来继续。</li><li>中断处理程序：</li></ol><ul><li>你站起来，走到门口（进入中断处理程序）。</li><li>签收快递并确认快递内容（处理中断）。</li></ul><ol start="5"><li>恢复现场：签收完快递后，你回到书桌前，继续之前的工作（恢复CPU现场，返回主程序）。</li></ol><p><strong>3.2 中断向量表</strong><br><img src="https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/67b0ba10d0e0a243d4ffb372.png" width=500></p>]]></content>
    
    
